@HostAddress = https://localhost:7168
@ApiKey = local-dev-key

### 0. Reset demo data for Dashboard and Agent demo
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/demo/reset
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 0-1. Dashboard summary after demo reset
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/summary
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 0-2. Agent pending approval contracts after demo reset
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/agent/contracts/pending-approval
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 0-3. Agent today work orders after demo reset
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/agent/workorders/today
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 0-4. Agent on-hold settlements after demo reset
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/agent/settlements/on-hold
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 0-5. Agent query after demo reset
### Source is controlled by Agent:Mode in appsettings. RuleBased returns "rule-based"; Ollama returns "ollama".
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/agent/query
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "현재 업무 현황 요약해줘"
}

### 1. Create contract (계약 등록)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/contracts
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contractNo": "CT-2026-0001",
  "customerName": "Sample Customer",
  "title": "Business Workflow Platform Contract",
  "amount": 12000000
}

### 2. Request contract approval (계약 승인 요청)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/contracts/1/request-approval
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestTitle": "Contract approval request",
  "requesterName": "FlowAI Manager",
  "approverName": "Approval Manager",
  "comment": "Please review this contract."
}

### 3. Approve contract and auto-create work order (계약 승인 및 작업 자동 생성)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/contracts/1/approve
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. Confirm auto-created work order (자동 생성된 작업 확인)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/work-orders
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 5. Start work order (작업 시작)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/work-orders/1/start
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 6. Complete work order (작업 완료)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/work-orders/1/complete
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 7. Request settlement (정산 요청)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/settlements
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workOrderId": 1,
  "settlementNo": "ST-2026-0001",
  "amount": 12000000
}

### 8. Start settlement review (정산 검토 시작)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/settlements/1/review
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 9. Approve settlement (정산 승인)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/settlements/1/approve
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 10. Request second settlement for hold test (보류 테스트용 두 번째 정산 요청)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/settlements
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workOrderId": 1,
  "settlementNo": "ST-2026-0002",
  "amount": 8000000
}

### 11. Start second settlement review (두 번째 정산 검토 시작)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/settlements/2/review
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 12. Hold second settlement (두 번째 정산 보류)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/settlements/2/hold
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "holdReason": "Amount verification required"
}

### 13. Request third settlement for reject test (반려 테스트용 세 번째 정산 요청)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/settlements
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workOrderId": 1,
  "settlementNo": "ST-2026-0003",
  "amount": 5000000
}

### 14. Start third settlement review (세 번째 정산 검토 시작)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/settlements/3/review
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 15. Reject third settlement (세 번째 정산 반려)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/settlements/3/reject
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rejectReason": "Supporting document is missing."
}

### 16. Dashboard summary (대시보드 업무 현황 요약)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/dashboard/summary
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 17. Agent customer status summary (Agent 고객사별 업무 상태 요약)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/agent/customers/Sample%20Customer/status-summary
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 18. Agent on-hold settlements (Agent 정산 보류 건 조회)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/agent/settlements/on-hold
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

### 19. Agent query dashboard summary (Agent 자연어 업무 현황 요약 질의)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/agent/query
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "현재 업무 현황 요약해줘"
}

### 20. Status history list (상태 변경 이력 조회)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/status-histories
X-FlowAI-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json
